	(4112,255,'_feedback_akismet_values','a:74:{s:14:\"comment_author\";s:11:\"John Murphy\";s:20:\"comment_author_email\";s:16:\"john@veetron.com\";s:18:\"comment_author_url\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"contact_form_subject\";s:38:\"Overvolted Contact Form - Reaching Out\";s:17:\"comment_author_IP\";s:14:\"108.61.228.127\";s:15:\"comment_content\";s:3305:\"Hi Overvolted\r\n\r\nFirst of all just wanted to say I have really enjoyed reading your website for a while and wanted to let you know about a project myself and a team have recently launched as it may possibly fit in with your site.\r\n\r\nWe currently have a project on Indiegogo for our VOMO Electric Scooter, http://igg.me/at/vomo/x/9873599 that is running for the next 30 days. I thought I might share it with you. Would you possibly be interested in doing a review on your site? Thanks for your time, and look forward to hearing for you. \r\n\r\nAlso any feedback you have would be much appreciated.  \r\n\r\nKind Regards,\r\n\r\nJohn\r\n\r\nI\'ve also pasted below our recent press release as this may help give you an idea of what it is all about. Thanks.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nFOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE: 21st June 2015\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nJohn Murphy                       \r\n\r\nVEETRON\r\n\r\njohn@veetron.com\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\nVEETRON Launches VOMO, The ultimate last mile electric vehicle \r\n\r\nVOMO is a high-powered 20mph foldable electric scooter with a launch offer price. \r\n\r\nHong Kong. 21st June 2015: VEETRON is proud to launch VOMO, the worldâ€™s most affordable high-powered electric scooter. A super compact foldable lightweight design, VOMO may just be the ultimate last mile transport vehicle.\r\n\r\nFinally a practical solution has arrived that offers the performance, design and affordability needed to make light electric vehicles a real viable alternative today.\r\n\r\nVOMO is equipped with a powerful rear wheel 350-watt motor with either an 8.8 or 11.6 amp Samsung Lithium Ion battery, providing speeds of 20 mph and a range of up to 25 miles.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nVOMO main features include:\r\n\r\nâ€¢          LCD Multifunction Display\r\n\r\nâ€¢          350W Hub Motor\r\n\r\nâ€¢          36v 8.8 or 11.6 Samsung Lithium Ion Battery\r\n\r\nâ€¢          Tubeless Inflatable 8x2 inch tires\r\n\r\nâ€¢          Color options, Matte Black or Aluminum Silver\r\n\r\nâ€¢          Top Speed of 20mph and range of 25 miles\r\n\r\nâ€¢          120mm Rear Disc brake with safety cut off.\r\n\r\nâ€¢          5 Power assist modes\r\n\r\nâ€¢          Safety start mode for accidental acceleration prevention\r\n\r\nâ€¢          Foldable carry or rolling design\r\n\r\nâ€¢          High strength yet lightweight aluminium components\r\n\r\nVOMO is available now for a special early offer price of $349 on Indiegogo, After that the price will go up to $549 MSRP, still an amazing price for such a powerful scooter with so many features. \r\n\r\nAbout VEETRON: VEETRON is committed to finally making light electric vehicles available to the average person and to make them a real viable transport alternative today. Based in Hong Kong with our design team and working closely with our manufacturing partners we are committed to pushing the boundaries of what is possible for light electric vehicles around the world. For over a year now we have been experimenting with many different materials, components and designs to finally create what VOMO is today, allowing it to have all the design features we wanted and at a price level to make it truly affordable. \r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\nLINKS:\r\n\r\nWebsite: http://veetron.com\r\n\r\nIndiegogo Page: http://igg.me/at/vomo/x/9873599\r\n\r\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/veetronofficial\r\n\r\nYouTube Video: https://youtu.be/Hwwc1GtcwSI\r\n\r\nImgur: (Free available images): http://veetron.imgur.com/ \r\n\r\n###\";s:12:\"comment_type\";s:12:\"contact_form\";s:7:\"user_ip\";s:14:\"108.61.228.127\";s:10:\"user_agent\";s:116:\"Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_10_3) AppleWebKit/600.6.3 (