m/en/us-aus/kalkhoff-na-models.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kalkhoff</a>/<a href=\"http://www.focus-bikes.com/us/en/home.html\" target=\"_blank\">Focus</a>, and the ever-ubiquitous <a href=\"http://www.currietech.com/haibike/\" target=\"_blank\">Haibike</a>. Or you can try your luck at having one of these shipped across the Atlantic, but we think that\'ll cost a pretty penny.','Blue Label Charger GT45','Ze Germans have produced a mean looking road machine, but is it available stateside?','inherit','open','open','','184-revision-v1','','','2015-06-16 00:04:02','2015-06-16 07:04:02','',184,'http://overvolted.com/184-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
