-1024x951.jpg\" alt=\"Google Specialized Turbo\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-238\" /><figcaption>Google\'s Asset Tracking barcode on a Specialized Turbo</figcaption></figure>\r\n\r\nAccording to Googler <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/116961301915403381264\" target=\"_blank\">Jacob Glick</a>, Google began testing out the Specialized Turbos with employees last year.\r\n\r\nJacob and Mike are hardly alone in their ebike use: Googler <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/106116111304373377701\" target=\"_blank\">Rob Russell</a> replied to Mike\'s post and noted that he\'s been quite happy commuting to the Googleplex on an ebike for the past few months.\r\n\r\nThis report indicates that electric bike usage is growing at a healthy pace at Google\'s headquarters, and Google\'s efforts to increase ebike use on their campus are likely paying dividends in reduced auto traffic, more efficient utilization of parking, and lower greenhouse gas emissions.\r\n\r\n<figure><img src=\"http://overvolted.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/VeniceDash-1024x752.jpg\" alt=\"2014 IZIP E3 Dash at Google Venice\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-240\" /><figcaption>A lone IZIP E3 Dash sits among employee bikes at Google\'s Venice, CA office</figcaption></figure>\r\n\r\nGoogle is also reportedly <a href=\"https://www.pedegoelectricbikes.com/pedegos-participation-at-googles-earth-day-celebration/\" target=\"_blank\">working with Pedego</a> and other ebike brands to study the use of ebikes on or near their campuses.\r\n\r\n<figure><img src=\"http://overvolted.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/pedegogoogle-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"pedegogoogle\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-229\" /><figcaption>A Pedego electric bike on Google\'s Mountain View campus</figcaption></figure>\r\n\r\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.seroundtable.com/photos/google-ebike-20451.html\" target=\"_blank\">Google Has An eBike Program - Search Engine Roundtable</a>','Google Rolls Out Ebikes To Their Mountain View Campus','Google\'s fleet of Specialized Turbos, in testing since last year, may now be available to ordinary Googlers.','inherit','open','open','','226-revision-v1','','','2015-06-18 15:24:02','2015-06-18 22:24:02','',226,'http://overvolted.com/226-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
