	(385,1,'2015-08-25 10:51:20','2015-08-25 17:51:20','Eurobike 2015 has just begun, and so begins the exciting deluge of product announcements.\r\n\r\nThe biggest ebike news so far is the announcement of the 2016 Stromer ST2-S model, which improves upon the ST2 by upgrading the battery capacity to 983Wh from the previous 814Wh, a 20% increase.\r\n\r\n<figure><img src=\"http://overvolted.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/ST2-2016-version.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Stromer ST2-S\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-386\" /><figcaption>The 2016 Stromer ST2-S</figcaption></figure>\r\n\r\nST2-S changes from the ST2:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>20%-larger 983Wh battery</li>\r\n	<li>Shimano Di2 electronic shifter</li>\r\n	<li>Dual beam headlights</li>\r\n	<li>Brooks Cambium saddle</li>\r\n	<li>New grey color option</li>\r\n	<li>New rims and red/white decals</li>\r\n	<li>1250-lumen Supernova M99 Pro headlight is 400% brighter than previous headlight</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nThe ST2 model also offers the new 983Wh battery as a &euro;410 option.\r\n\r\n<figure><img src=\"http://overvolted.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/m99pro.jpg\" alt=\"Supernova M99 Pro Ebike Headlight\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-387\" /><figcaption>Supernova M99 Pro Ebike Headlight</figcaption></figure>\r\n\r\nHere\'s the pricing for Germany (with the headlight purposefully obfuscated):\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://overvolted.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/ST2-2016-709x1024.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Stromer ST2 Price\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-388\" />\r\n\r\nBig thanks to ebike crusader Ravi Kempaiah for <a href=\"http://electricbikereview.com/community/threads/stromer-st2-2016-model.2617/\" target=\"_blank\">posting this news first</a>!','The 2016 Stromer ST2 and ST2-S','On the first day of Eurobike, Stromer announced its new top-line ST2-S.','publish','open','open','','the-2016-stromer-st2-and-st2-s','','','2015-08-25 10:51:20','2015-08-25 17:51:20','',0,'http://overvolted.com/?p=385',0,'post','',2),
