	(688,1,'2015-09-30 13:57:43','2015-09-30 20:57:43','Today, I paid a visit to the friendly team at <a href=\"http://www.electricbikeattack.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Electric Bike Attack+ in Santa Monica</a>, just two blocks from the beach and only 15 miles west of Downtown Los Angeles.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://overvolted.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_5645.jpg\" alt=\"Bike Attack Electric, Santa Monica, CA\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-661\" />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.electricbikeattack.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Electric Bike Attack+</a> opened in February 2015 and has a sister shop, <a href=\"http://www.bikeattack.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Bike Attack</a>, that has operated in the area for 20 years and primarily sells traditional bicycles.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://overvolted.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_5648.jpg\" alt=\"Stromer Electric Bikes at Electric Bike Attack in Santa Monica, CA\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-662\" />\r\n\r\nElectric Bike Attack+ is the largest Stromer dealer in Southern California and has many Stromer ST1s and Stromer ST2s in stock, so if you\'re looking to test drive a Stromer in Los Angeles, Electric Bike Attack should be your starting point. The shop also stocks the very popular Easy Motion line of bikes, and is also certified to service Bosch and Bionx systems. Here\'s a full list of the brands carried at Bike Attack Electric+:\r\n\r\n<strong>Brands Carried At Electric Bike Attack+</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Stromer</li>\r\n	<li>Easy Motion</li>\r\n	<li>Focus</li>\r\n	<li>Kalkhoff</li>\r\n	<li>Felt</li>\r\n	<li>A2B</li>\r\n	<li>OHM</li>\r\n	<li>BESV</li>\r\n	<li>Cannondale</li>\r\n	<li>Bionx</li>\r\n	<li>Mando</li>\r\n	<li>eLux</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://overvolted.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_5656.jpg\" alt=\"Easy Motion and Felt Electric Bicycles at Electric Bike Attack in Santa Monica, CA\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-668\" />\r\n\r\nCo-owner Andrew Smith says that Electric Bike Attack+ aims to be highest quality ebike shop in L.A., to carry the best brands, and to offer the best customer service, and though the shop is picky about what brands it chooses to sell, Bike Attack Electric+ will service any brand of electric bike. Smith reports that his shop has performed service on quite a few low-cost Sondors electric bikes, mirroring the experience of <a href=\"http://motostrano.com\" target=\"_blank\">Bay Area ebike dealer Motostrano</a>, which has also seen customers bring in their Sondors ebikes for assembly and/or service.\r\n\r\n<figure><img src=\"http://overvolted.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_5667-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"A Cannondale Lefty Electric Bike at Electric Bike Attack in Santa Monica, CA\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-675\" /><figcaption>A 2016 Cannondale Lefty electric bike at Electric Bike Attack+</figcaption></figure>\r\n\r\nElectric Bike Attack\'s customers range from bike messengers to weekend warriors, and Electric Bike Attack fits in quite well with L.A.\'s Westside neighborhoods, which have convenient beachside bicycle paths and lots of people riding around on beach cruisers. Electric Bike Attack also carries a selection of fatbikes from Felt and ELUX which can also be ridden on sand, and which would serve as decent solutions to transport surfboards between home and the beach (with a purpose-built surfboard cargo carrier, obviously).\r\n\r\n<div class=\"hide-for-large-up text-center\">\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3307.7249387224565!2d-118.48175800132756!3d33.99959826122189!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x80c2bad219c85483%3A0x2f7a8e987af6fdbe!2sBike+Attack+Electric%2B!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1443642949842\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"show-for-large-up text-center\">\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3307.72493872